* Specify target to sniff
@code bash
sudo airodump-ng wlan1mon -c 3 -w wpa --essid KPN235434 --bssid 34:08:04:09:3D:38
@end
** We need to make sure that the AUTH is PSK because this does not work for MGT (Enterprise)

